item.title: GSBR: Gyroscope Self-Balancing Robot Final Report
item.description: Not W A L L-E The Gyroscope Self-Balancing Robot (GSBR) project has ended. Previous posts on the progress and results can be found on this site. A more detailed and better edited look at the project can be found in the final report that the team has written up here or as a download here. The source code and testing code can all be found at the Github page here.
